reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best Cord You Need - Quality and Durability
reviews.reviewText: 5 Star Review -The product works perfectly as designed. The cable is very flexible which is very important when constantly connecting and disconnecting it. The braided sections are very well knit together and helps more flexibility. Over time the standard cables get discolored and sticky but this is almost a cloth feeling and stays perfectly in shape. It also matches well with my car interior and looks uniform with the molding on the pillars. I would highly recommend this product. The speed of charging and connectivity is great. I am using it for fast charging and also car play. The only issue I have is that I misplaced one of the two cables it comes with in the box. Not sure where it's gone! The seller is great to work with and they offer support as needed.
